quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  43,74,"Inna almujrimeena fee AAathabijahannama khalidoon"
  43,75,"La yufattaru AAanhum wahum feehimublisoon"
  43,76,"Wama thalamnahumwalakin kanoo humu aththalimeen"
  43,77,"Wanadaw ya maliku liyaqdiAAalayna rabbuka qala innakum makithoon"
  43,78,"Laqad ji/nakum bilhaqqiwalakinna aktharakum lilhaqqi karihoon"
  43,79,"Am abramoo amran fa-inna mubrimoon"
  43,80,"Am yahsaboona anna lanasmaAAu sirrahum wanajwahum bala warusulunaladayhim yaktuboon"
  43,81,"Qul in kana lirrahmaniwaladun faana awwalu alAAabideen"
  43,82,"Subhana rabbi assamawatiwal-ardi rabbi alAAarshi AAamma yasifoon"
  43,83,"Fatharhum yakhoodoowayalAAaboo hatta yulaqoo yawmahumu allatheeyooAAadoon"
  43,84,"Wahuwa allathee fee assama-iilahun wafee al-ardi ilahun wahuwa alhakeemualAAaleem"
  43,85,"Watabaraka allathee lahu mulkuassamawati wal-ardi wamabaynahuma waAAindahu AAilmu assaAAatiwa-ilayhi turjaAAoon"
  43,86,"Wala yamliku allatheenayadAAoona min doonihi ashshafaAAata illaman shahida bilhaqqi wahum yaAAlamoon"
  43,87,"Wala-in saaltahum man khalaqahumlayaqoolunna Allahu faanna yu/fakoon"
  43,88,"Waqeelihi ya rabbi inna haola-iqawmun la yu/minoon"
  43,89,"Fasfah AAanhum waqulsalamun fasawfa yaAAlamoon"
